UC3 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC4 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC5 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC6 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC8 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC9 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC10 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen
UC11 <|-- UC1 #SeaGreen

@enduml